{"type":"article","id":15180,"title":"【過街老鼠】林鄭與十多名便衣落區遭居民粗口回應","uid":30048,"topics":[17,3160,2573,6861],"contents":"（注意：文內包含柒婆照片）<br>\n<br>\n下午2時半，一部AM90私家車停泊在汝州街，<u>多名交通警、交通督導員到來趕車</u>，其後見林鄭穿上白色外套、黑長褲，由桂林街38A一幢唐樓落樓，<u>有至少10多名便衣警務人員及G4人員包圍着她</u>，其間沒有街坊理會她，一名老翁更與她擦身而過，林鄭戴上口罩，向在場人士揮手說「大家辛苦啦」，卻換來<b>街坊粗話回應</b>。林鄭最後登車離開。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YQ5Elzv.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YQ5Elzv.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YQ5Elzv.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TuqmC5g.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TuqmC5g.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TuqmC5g.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hdRtNY.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hdRtNY.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hdRtNY.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n來源：https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200225/GKESWX6Z2PHQWRHIY44TPQAQ7Y/<br>\n<br>\n同場加映：<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%87%E9%A6%96%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">林鄭民望再創新低　支持率首跌至單位數（Stand News 立場新聞）</a>","date":"2020-02-26","agreeCount":26,"discussionCount":0}